<span id="freeTextContainer4999518694926031969">I enjoyed the twist on this tremendously. The roles Georgiana and Anne play are so fascinating and funny. I enjoyed the assertions/possibilities filled in that the original Pride and Prejudice left for our imagination of timing, acquaintances, etc. It&apos;s not very descriptive of scenery etc but each story fills a different niche. I enjoyed the plotting, planning and tension in the relationships as well as seeing a totally different side of Anne. Georgiana is maturing as a young woman should. There</span>
  <span id="freeText4999518694926031969" style="display:none">I enjoyed the twist on this tremendously. The roles Georgiana and Anne play are so fascinating and funny. I enjoyed the assertions/possibilities filled in that the original Pride and Prejudice left for our imagination of timing, acquaintances, etc. It's not very descriptive of scenery etc but each story fills a different niche. I enjoyed the plotting, planning and tension in the relationships as well as seeing a totally different side of Anne. Georgiana is maturing as a young woman should. There were times when I just couldn't put it down.</span>
