      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9781402261473" href="/book/show/10224698-the-perfect-bride-for-mr-darcy">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55979788-j-w-garrett?shelf=jaff-pride-and-prejudice">jaff-pride-and-prejudice</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55979788-j-w-garrett?shelf=2016">2016</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55979788-j-w-garrett?shelf=era-6-regency-1811-1820">era-6-regency-1811-1820</a>, 
