        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3347216514" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15978486413215102173">I really enjoyed the book. For some who love the original Pride and Prejudice, there can never be an equal. I agree. But I sure enjoy the variations! And this variation is cute, sweet, and fun. I liked some of the new characters in this book, and enjoyed Ann and Georgiana immensely. I have to admit that I wasn&apos;t a fan of the past paramours mentioned. Nice read!</span>
  <span id="freeText15978486413215102173" style="display:none">I really enjoyed the book. For some who love the original Pride and Prejudice, there can never be an equal. I agree. But I sure enjoy the variations! And this variation is cute, sweet, and fun. I liked some of the new characters in this book, and enjoyed Ann and Georgiana immensely. I have to admit that I wasn't a fan of the past paramours mentioned. Nice read!</span>
